---
---
<style>
  .hero-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 6rem 1rem 4rem 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  /* Subtle Background Glow */
  .hero-background {
    position: absolute;
    top: -20%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15) 0%, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0) 70%);
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .pill-badge {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    z-index: 1;
    transition: background 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none !important;
  }
  .pill-badge:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4.5rem) !important;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-align: center;
    color: #ffffff;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0 !important;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .hero-title span {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #60a5fa, #a78bfa);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #94a3b8;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 0 3rem 0;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none !important;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #0f172a !important;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #f8fafc;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px -2px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }
  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: #ffffff !important;
    border: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-color: #475569;
  }

  /* macOS Terminal Window */
  .terminal {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 900px;
    background: #0f111a;
    border: 1px solid #1e293b;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    z-index: 1;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .terminal-header {
    background: #1e293b;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .traffic-light {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .red { background: #ef4444; }
  .yellow { background: #eab308; }
  .green { background: #22c55e; }
  
  .terminal-body {
    padding: 2rem;
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #e2e8f0;
  }
  .user-msg {
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .ai-header {
    color: #60a5fa;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .tool-call {
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
    color: #38bdf8;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
  }
  .text-muted { color: #64748b; font-weight: bold; }
</style>

<div class="hero-wrapper">
  <div class="hero-background"></div>
  
  <a href="https://github.com/avenka29/cortex" class="pill-badge">
    🎉 Introducing Cortex v0.1.4 <span>&rarr;</span>
  </a>

  <h1 class="hero-title">
    The Domain-Driven Brain for your <span>AI Assistant</span>
  </h1>
  
  <p class="hero-subtitle">
    Supercharge Claude and Cursor with a strict Topological Graph and a lightning-fast SQLite Vector Database. Run entirely on localhost.
  </p>

  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="/cortex/getting-started/" class="btn btn-primary">
      Get Started
    </a>
    <a href="https://github.com/avenka29/cortex" class="btn btn-secondary">
      View GitHub
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="terminal">
    <div class="terminal-header">
      <div class="traffic-light red"></div>
      <div class="traffic-light yellow"></div>
      <div class="traffic-light green"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="terminal-body">
      <div class="user-msg">
        <span class="text-muted">❯ User:</span> I need to add a new authentication endpoint. Where does the auth logic live?
      </div>
      
      <div class="ai-msg">
        <div class="ai-header">🤖 Claude</div>
        <div class="tool-call">⚡ Tool: semantic_search("authentication logic")</div><br/>
        Based on your Cortex Vector Database, the authentication logic is documented in `docs/auth.md` and belongs to the **AuthService** component.<br/><br/>
        
        <div class="tool-call">⚡ Tool: get_blast_radius("AuthService")</div><br/>
        If we modify the AuthService, we will also need to test the **UserController** and **PaymentGateway** components, as they strictly depend on it according to your Topological Graph.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
